<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thanks for requesting a business insurance quote from Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Due to your job role and industry, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">we require some more information in order to complete your quote</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>I have been calling you today, so we can get the additional details we need from you. Unfortunately, I have not been able to reach you.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>If you are still interested in moving forward, please give me a call on 01242 808 740</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>I look forward to speaking with you.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808740</span></p>]]></td>
